        {
            "id": 6007566,
            "title": "國台辦宣布：對台獨頑固分子沈伯洋關聯企業予以懲戒",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大陸國務院台辦發言人朱鳳蓮周四（5 日）表示，經查，「台獨」頑固分子沈伯洋之父沈土城，在台灣企業兆億有限公司擔任負責人，該公司與大陸某些企業存在貿易往來與業務合作，從中謀取經濟利益。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007566%2Fl%2F6829ffae54310c7534220ae12bb30911.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">大陸國務院台辦發言人朱鳳蓮。（圖：今日海峽）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>朱鳳蓮說，大陸方面決不允許「台獨」頑固分子關聯企業在大陸謀利，決定對兆億實施懲戒，禁止其與大陸組織、企業、個人進行任何交易、合作，並將對其採取其他必要措施。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
